					Write some text here to explain the features of your site or application, it
					has lots of uses.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 image">
        <%= image_tag "feature2.png", class: "img-responsive", alt: "feature2" %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>		
</div>

